<!--<h4>Piece I</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> sakalalokaccakra</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>va<hi rend="grantha">rtti śrī Irāja</hi>nā<hi rend="grantha">rā</hi>yaṇa (campu)
<lb n="3" break="no"/>campuvarāyaṟku yāṇṭu patiṉ
</p>

<!--<h4>Piece II</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1" break="no"/>—vitta Attimallanāyakarkku tiruamutupaṭikku
<lb n="2"/>m tirunāḷpaṭikkum tirumaṭaippaḷḷippuṟamā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ka tai mā<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>m piṟanta nāyaṟṟukkiḻamaiyum <hi rend="grantha">mṛ</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">gaśirṣa</hi>mum peṟṟa Aṉṟu viṭṭa nuḷampaicciṟ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṟeriyāna Aḻakiyanāyanallūr nāṟpālellaik
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kuḷpaṭṭa naṉce<supplied reason="omitted">y</supplied> puṉce<supplied reason="omitted">y</supplied> nilamum menokkiṉa mara
<lb n="7" break="no"/>mum kiṇokkiṉa kiṇaṟum pāṭikāvaluḷḷiṭṭa—
</p>

